# Tests that a graph can be created, four nodes and
# five edges that create a loop can be added, 
# and four nodes and five edges can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing4

# Add four nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing4 Frodo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing4 Gandalf
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing4 Samwise
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing4 Arwin

# Add five edges
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing4 Gandalf Frodo TheHobbit
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing4 Frodo Samwise TheReturnOfTheKing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing4 Frodo Samwise TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing4 Samwise Arwin TheFellowshipOfTheRing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing4 Arwin Gandalf TheFellowshipOfTheRing

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Frodo, Gandalf, Arwin, Samwise
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing4
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing4 Frodo
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing4 Gandalf
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing4 Arwin
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing4 Samwise